name: Get-Jacked!!
description:
A Fitness 3D Clicker Experience!

Are you ready to Get Jacked ??

Punch and destroy fruits with your buddy Jerome to develop the biggest arms possible!!

 

One of your Five a Day!

Meet an eclectic cast of characters who will generate nutrients and help you become the best!!

 

Push it to the Limit!

Accumulate resources to buy super-powered protein shakes and upgrade your strength!!

 

A game created by Max Elmore with the assistance of many.

A Solar Flare London Production.
